    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "At Lat. 28°13' N. Long. 177°22' W. (Pacific\nOcean), from some undiscovered point in the\nAlêutian Islands comes the solemn and serious\ngony (Laysan Albatross) for the mating and\nhatching\nseason.\nThe gony is a picturesque\nvisitor from November to\nJune at Midway\nIsland, unique stopping point on Pan American\nAirways 9,000-mile transpacific airline.\nALALWED AT\nMIDDAY ISLAND\n-PA TEIC O SEAN-\n17H014\n-EF,\nNUV\nARD\nFIRSi\nSADORESS™\n30 CENTS 30\n1940\nCANCELLATION\nMAK. FURIE\n2073 Oglen St.\nDenies, Colo. V. 2.4"
    ],
